fields.search:
SELECT tag_lastfm, sum(listeners_lastfm) as sum_linsteners
FROM artists.artists lateral view explode(split(tags_lastfm,';')) tags_lastfm AS tag_lastfm GROUP BY tag_lastfm ORDER BY sum_linsteners DESC LIMIT 1;
